<section class="about-profile" aria-label="About Ahmed Loudghiri">
  <%= image_tag "ahmed.png", alt: "Portrait of Ahmed Loudghiri", class: "about-profile__photo", loading: "lazy" %>
  <div class="about-profile__body prose">
    <p>
      I'm Ahmed Loudghiri. I build software at the intersection of product,
      AI, and games. I currently lead <strong>ToutiGame</strong>, where we
      are designing a games platform around play, identity, and ownership.
    </p>
    <p>
      Most days I move between backend systems, frontend craft, and AI
      tooling. I care about taste, durability, and small interfaces that
      quietly do a lot.
    </p>
    <p>
      This site is a personal operating system. A place for writing,
      projects, experiments, and the decision logs behind them. It will
      keep growing in small, deliberate steps.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
